{"tid":2027442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[巴西龜]急！龜龜受傷，求有愛龜人士解答","createTime":"2020-05-21T11:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T11:01:25.000Z","uid":252694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"653ddcd0ff1bab1a2e239f98057e18870ef211d0","tid":2027442,"uid":252694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，想向各位請教一下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期日帶左巴西龜去屋企樓下散步，散步後發現佢擦傷左雙腿，即刻帶去水族店，店員建議我買一支龜康寧幫龜龜搽擦傷既地方（然後我每天都有係擦傷的地方用棉花棒搽，再等15至20分鐘至放番入缸，亦在水缸滴左幾滴龜康寧 ）唔知道係咪因為支藥水本身是紅色，所以搽完之後擦傷的地方就染紅厫，想請教各位究竟係龜龜傷口發炎，定係藥水的功效。頭兩張是龜龜剛擦傷時既情況，後兩張是4天後而家情況（有每日搽龜康寧 ）。現時龜龜既狀況都係同平時一樣，沒有異樣（正常進食，活潑，有大便）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A42PLdA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA42PLdA.jpg&h=ae5aa5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvyZ7rX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvyZ7rX.jpg&h=833c610f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tU0mBko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtU0mBko.png&h=0d9e9332&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g08zbTO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg08zbTO.png&h=c2f32afb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43a2730b10d9d9e092d5376dcdbc917ae4c55f7c","tid":2027442,"uid":216975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:45:01.000Z","msg":"好易引膿 你要做消毒<br />\n買枝合脈碘酒開稀浸十五分鐘  或者直送滴傷口但佢會痛"},{"pid":"9afaef47951ab1f851bfd1fc0dfdd0657f6be146","tid":2027442,"uid":3390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:39:01.000Z","msg":"碘酒搽傷口 乾養 食野先落水"},{"pid":"c31f8ce529b1f45a13873997add4c994b2012080","tid":2027442,"uid":252694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9afaef47951ab1f851bfd1fc0dfdd0657f6be146","tid":2027442,"uid":3390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:39:01.000Z","msg":"碘酒搽傷口 乾養 食野先落水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"宜家查完藥，幫佢乾養緊，清左個缸啲水，放咗幾條毛巾俾佢。但係佢係咁喺度掙扎，係咁撞落啲玻璃度好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}